data.description: Discover unparalleled luxury living within the coveted gated community of Artesia. This beautifully maintained property is nestled minutes from the prestigious Sawgrass Mall, Amerant Arena, and an array of upscale dining and shopping options at the Colonnade Outlets. Situated just 4 miles away from one of South Florida's top-ranked private schools, American Heritage.Immerse yourself in resort-style living with a captivating pool and spa for ultimate relaxation. Boasting an indoor basketball court, gym, tennis/pickleball courts, as well as club and conference rooms, ensuring there's something for everyone, this property seamlessly combines luxury with convenience.
